India’s finest in the making!
These designers are rewriting the fashion rulebook and putting Indian artistry on the world map. Tap to see their inspiring work!

#FutureOfIndianFashion #BoldDesigners #FEF #HeritageMeetsInnovation #GlobalStage #TimelessPioneers

Supriya Lele, @supriya_lele, is known for seamlessly fusing contemporary Western aesthetics with traditional Indian textiles, such as khadi and handloom fabrics, making her work highly unique in the modern fashion landscape. Her collections have captivated attention of global fashion figures, especially with her innovative approach to gender-neutral clothing.

#SupriyaLele #ModernIndianFashion #FEF #HeritageWithInnovation #GlobalDesignImpact

Celebrating start-ups that dare to dream big. On #NationalStartupDay, hear from Sanjay Nigam, the visionary behind Fashion Entrepreneur Fund, as he shares how FEF is building a platform for innovation and creativity in the world of fashion.

Suede isn’t just for winter, it’s a year-round style hero! From stylish jackets in the colder months to chic skirts and boots for spring and autumn, this versatile fabric works for any season. Add its timeless texture to your wardrobe for effortless elegance all year round.

#FEFRecommends #FashionEntrepreneurFund #SuedeFashion

Animal print, plaid, sequins, boho ruffles, and suede, 2024’s iconic styles are still leaving their mark in 2025. Bold, timeless, sparkling, free-spirited, edgy, there’s a trend for everyone. At Fashion Entrepreneur Fund, we help turn your style vision into something truly unique. 

Which trend resonates with you?
